skdetail:

Invocation Name: make me laugh
des:
Need laughter therapy?? Alexa got you covered. 
Enable "Make Me Laugh" skill and then, Invoke by saying "run make me laugh" or "tell me something funny".

Because doctors say, "LAUGHTER IS THE BEST MEDICINE".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
